name: Dorheek
content:
Dorheek was a male Kubaz who lived during the Cold War between the Galactic Republic and the resurgent Sith Empire. During the war, he worked as a merchant on the planet Nal Hutta, the adopted homeworld of Hutt species. Whilst at the stall the Kubaz wore a pair of goggles with red lenses to protect his eyes as well as blue shirt and pants. Dorheek had grey skin and purple hair.
Dorheek first appeared in the video game Star Wars: The Old Republic released by BioWare in 2011. He appears as a social items vendor on the planet Nal Hutta, the starting planet for players of the bounty hunter and Imperial Agent class.
